Package com.mapzen.tangram.networking

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HttpHandler
    HttpHandler interface for handling network requests for map resources, it can be implemented to provide non-default http network request or caching behavior.
    HttpHandler.Callback
    Callback Passes network responses from underlying implementation to be processed internally
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultHttpHandler
    DefaultHttpHandler is an implementation of HttpHandler using OkHTTP.
